author: Tabletop Minions
description:
And it's not only the crazy-looking Horus Heresy terminators, either: I haven't seen a new model for Warhammer 40,000 or Horus Heresy that has "spoke" to me in some time. But Age of Sigmar and even The Old World have been KILLING it (hello Cathay). So what gives? I'll talk about that, and of course I'll answer your wargaming-related questions. Come have fun!

Vince Venturella and I made ANOTHER game! Check out Reign in Iron - miniatures-agnostic robot vs. demon skirmish combat at http://www.reigninirongame.com

I'm a member of The Army Painter Factory Team - and I'm passing the savings on to you! Use code 'FactoryUncle5' at checkout to get 5% off of your entire order at http://www.thearmypainter.com or check my favorite Army Painter products at https://thearmypainter.com/tabletop-minions

I'm now a partner on Twitch! I paint minis every Friday morning and Monday night, and sometimes take paint breaks (play video games poorly). Follow me: http://www.twitch.tv/tabletopminions
